    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《南瓜餐厅》会显示在屏幕的底部并自动化经营，您只需要准备足够的食材后就可以去忙别的事情了。当然不要忘记把赚到的金币继续发展餐厅，以此提高餐厅的盈利效率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/1f703f3398c999f8bc3da0c294a5b2be.poster.avif?t=1754781702\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/1f703f3398c999f8bc3da0c294a5b2be.webm?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/1f703f3398c999f8bc3da0c294a5b2be.mp4?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/9b0d8e13ec4edad3e1e823b6915a2e99.webp?t=1754781702\" width=117 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食材是维持餐厅运转的必要资源，在食材价格低廉的时候多多囤货，价格处于高位时就暂且观望（或者刷新一下？）低买高卖才能获取更多利润。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/0b78e1ba65436ba5086ef7636973f4e8.webp?t=1754781702\" width=117 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >商店出售着各种类型的食谱，购买后可以将其设置为餐厅推荐菜式，客人就会更多的选择你推荐的食物噢，当然有时他们也会选择其他的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/d89e5d506208a58c7f5c052c6c5ed75a.webp?t=1754781702\" width=117 height=35 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >员工的能力决定了餐厅的运转效率，多多招聘优秀的员工并且不要忘记给他们升级噢！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >员工偶尔也会摸鱼不干活，此时你可以用锤子重重地敲打他们！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 你也可以给修改每个员工的名字，让你喜欢（或者讨厌）的人来给你的餐厅打工吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/a65df0171cdb70fec92240d3ddf7bf86.poster.avif?t=1754781702\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/a65df0171cdb70fec92240d3ddf7bf86.webm?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/a65df0171cdb70fec92240d3ddf7bf86.mp4?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/497bf29b9669d01d8760f2f94584e9bd.webp?t=1754781702\" width=117 height=31 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富的装饰物除了用来点缀餐厅之外，还能够提升客人的打赏概率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你还能够自由更换餐厅的样式（包括房梁、墙面和地板），通过不同颜色和纹理的样式组合搭建你独具特色的餐厅风格吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/2486c467f740fdc4184ce4a07269d45d.poster.avif?t=1754781702\" width=720 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/2486c467f740fdc4184ce4a07269d45d.webm?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231690/extras/2486c467f740fdc4184ce4a07269d45d.mp4?t=1754781702\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
